about.description: Python implementation of the Mixed-Scale Dense Convolutional Neural Network.
about.summary: Python implementation of the Mixed-Scale Dense Convolutional Neural Network.

name: msdnet
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "msdnet" %}
{% set version = "1.0.0" %}

package:
  name: {{ name|lower }}
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  url: https://github.com/dmpelt/{{ name }}/archive/v{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: e1e9f53cb662f6368a0389ca9a99583f8e964cef2c53f83742f6466e02d26562

build:
  number: 0
  skip: True  # [py<36]
  script: {{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . -vv  # [linux]
  script: {{ PYTHON }} setup.py bdist_wheel --plat-name macosx-10.9-x86_64 && pip install --no-index --find-links=dist msdnet  # [osx]
  script: {{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . -vv --install-option=--generator --install-option="NMake Makefiles"  # [win]

requirements:
  build:
    - {{ compiler('c') }}
  host:
    - python
    - pip
    - setuptools
    - scikit-build
    - openmp
  run:
    - python
    - numpy >=1.12
    - tifffile
    - scikit-image
    - psutil
    - h5py
    - tqdm
    - numba >=0.41
    - cudatoolkit
    - imageio
    - openmp

test:
  imports:
    - msdnet

about:
  home: http://github.com/dmpelt/msdnet
  license: MIT
  license_family: MIT
  license_file: LICENSE
  summary: 'Python implementation of the Mixed-Scale Dense Convolutional Neural Network.'

  description: |
    Python implementation of the Mixed-Scale Dense Convolutional Neural Network.
  doc_url: http://dmpelt.github.io/msdnet
  dev_url: https://github.com/dmpelt/msdnet

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - dmpelt
